# ==============================================================================
# DOCKER CONTEXT ARCHITECTURAL MANIFEST (.dockerignore)
# SUBSTRATE: Self-Optimizing AGI Substrate
# PROTOCOL: Siphon-Based Evolution Strict Gatekeeping
# ==============================================================================

# [1] CONSTITUTIONAL GATEKEEPING: SECRETS & VCS
# Immediate extermination of credential leakage and history bloat. Deviations halt execution.
**/.git
**/.gitmodules
**/.gitignore
**/.github
**/.svn
**/.env*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.cert
**/*.crt
**/.npmrc
**/.yarnrc
**/.aws-sam

# [2] ADAPTIVE EXECUTION STATE: BUILD CACHES & TRANSIENT DATA
# Eradicating speculative mechanisms and transient build states to ensure deterministic builds.
**/node_modules
**/.npm
**/.yarn
**/.pnpm-store
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.next
**/.nuxt
**/.cache
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.map
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
**/venv
**/env
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.tox
**/.nox
**/.ipynb_checkpoints

# [3] NEXUS EVALUATORS: FIDELITY EVALUATION FRAGMENTS
# Testing logic and local fidelity gates are isolated from the production substrate context.
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test
**/tests
**/__tests__
**/specs
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.js
**/jest.config.*
**/vitest.config.*
**/nosetests.xml
**/coverage.xml
**/.pytest.ini

# [4] SIPHON FORENSICS: LOCAL TELEMETRY & OBSERVABILITY
# Local logs and trace artifacts are excluded to prevent context contamination. 
# Trace visibility must be strictly bound to remote telemetry.
**/logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pip-log.txt
**/.genkit
**/trace-dumps
**/pids
**/*.pid
**/*.seed
**/*.pid.lock

# [5] ARCHITECTURAL BYPRODUCTS: IDE & SYSTEM METADATA
# Substrate independence requires total decoupling from host-specific configurations.
**/.vscode
**/.vscode-test
**/.idea
**/.eclipse
**/.settings
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.directory
**/tmp
**/temp
**/transient
**/*.bak

# [6] SIPHON SOURCE DATABASES: HEAVY ASSETS
# Excluding heavy ML/AI datasets and weights not meant for the raw container layer.
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db
**/*.onnx
**/*.safetensors
**/*.ckpt
**/*.h5
**/*.pb
**/datasets
**/models/weights
**/checkpoints

# [7] INFRASTRUCTURE & ORCHESTRATION OVERRIDES
# Excluding local compose, kube configs, and terraform states from context payload.
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/docker-compose*.yaml
**/.kube
**/kubernetes
**/*.tfstate*
**/.terraform
**/*.tfvars

# [8] EXPLICIT INCLUSIONS (BINDING MAP WHITELIST)
# Rigidly injecting required configuration files for Governance Instance and Observability bindings.
!GACR/AIM.json
!CMR.json
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!yarn.lock
!pnpm-lock.yaml
!requirements.txt
!pyproject.toml
!tsconfig.json
!src/
